  "text": "making a splash..."
 },
 {
  "i": 31,
  "style": "Title",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(2000,2000)}Perona's Terror!\\NUsopp vs. the Ghost Princess!"
 },
 {
  "i": 32,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You..."
 },
 {
  "i": 33,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "How come you can fly?"
 },
 {
  "i": 34,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Such confidence..."
 },
 {
  "i": 35,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You were running away from me a while ago..."
 },
 {
  "i": 36,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Why the sudden change?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 37,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "I was a bit distracted a while ago."
 },
 {
  "i": 38,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "I never thought someone immune to the negative ghosts could exist."
 },
 {
  "i": 39,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "I have only one thing to tell you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 40,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Cheer up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 41,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 42,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "So what if you can fly?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 43,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm a sniper!"
 },
 {
  "i": 44,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Whether you fly or dance, I don't care!"
 },
 {
  "i": 45,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Allow me to explain!"
 },
 {
  "i": 46,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "My new weapon Kabuto gains both range and stability thanks to these five axes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 47,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "When the Breath Dials I got from Sky Island are activated at the moment of firing,"
 },
 {
  "i": 48,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "rotation is added to the bullet, making all kinds of speed changes possible, creating a Super Pachinko!"
 },
 {
  "i": 49,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Flame, flash, impact."
 },
 {
  "i": 50,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "By changing the dials, I can make the bullets stronger!"
 },
 {
  "i": 51,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "No one can escape its abilities!"
 },
 {
  "i": 52,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Now, prepare yo-"
 },
 {
  "i": 53,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "She's gone!"
 },
 {
  "i": 54,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Where'd she go?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 55,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Behind you."
 },
 {
  "i": 56,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Hurry and try to hit me."
 },
 {
  "i": 57,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "W-What the hell are you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 58,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You damn..."
 },
 {
  "i": 59,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Deadly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 60,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Swallowtail Meteor!"
 },
 {
  "i": 61,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "She went back to normal!"
 },
 {
  "i": 62,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You..."
 },
 {
  "i": 63,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm gonna shoot you down!"
 },
 {
  "i": 64,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Mantis Meteor!"
 },
 {
  "i": 65,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Her hands are sinking into my body!"
 },
 {
  "i": 66,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "H-How come?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 67,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I don't even feel pain!"
 },
 {
  "i": 68,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm..."
 },
 {
  "i": 69,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Already... done for!"
 },
 {
  "i": 70,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "You fool, look closer."
 },
 {
  "i": 71,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "There's no external wound."
 },
 {
  "i": 72,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "My hands are just inside your body."
 },
 {
  "i": 73,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "It means your death is at hand."
 },
 {
  "i": 74,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Right now, with my own hands, I'm going to..."
 },
 {
  "i": 75,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "crush your heart."
 },
 {
  "i": 76,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 77,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Please stop it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 78,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That'd kill me for real!"
 },
 {
  "i": 79,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I'm going to kill you."
 },
 {
  "i": 80,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Now..."
 },
 {
  "i": 81,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Die in agonizing pain!"
 },
 {
  "i": 82,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "No!"
 },
 {
  "i": 83,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Please stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 84,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I don't want to...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 85,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Of course I can't do such a thing."
 },
 {
  "i": 86,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "A bluff?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 87,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\move(640,700,640,643,700,1100)}I hit my head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 88,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "If I had the ability to do physical harm like crushing..."
 },
 {
  "i": 89,
  "style": "Secondary",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I hit my head!"
 },
 {
  "i": 90,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "You would have died the instant my hands went into your body."
 },
 {
  "i": 91,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Either way, this is bad for the heart."
 },
 {
  "i": 92,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I just went through..."
 },
 {
  "i": 93,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Your body."
 },
 {
  "i": 94,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Even though you can see me clearly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 95,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "My body can go through anything."
 },
 {
  "i": 96,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Deadly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 97,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(0,150)}Six Chain Viper Star!"
 },
 {
  "i": 98,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Didn't I just tell you I can go through anything?"
 },
 {
  "i": 99,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 100,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's creepy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 101,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "In other words, your attacks can't hit me."
 },
 {
  "i": 102,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 103,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Go away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 104,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Damn!"
 },
 {
  "i": 105,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Stay away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 106,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Go away, damn it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 107,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "What're you gonna do now?"
 },
 {
  "i": 108,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Your attacks have no effect."
 },
 {
  "i": 109,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 110,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You bluffed about crushing my heart a while ago!"
 },
 {
  "i": 111,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "In that case, you can't touch me either!"
 },
 {
  "i": 112,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You can't attack me either!"
 },
 {
  "i": 113,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You can't attack!"
 },
 {
  "i": 114,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Right?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 115,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Mini Hollow..."
 },
 {
  "i": 116,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "W-What is that?"
 },
 {
  "i": 117,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,50)}Ghost Rap..."
 },
 {
  "i": 118,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "T-The... wall...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 119,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "A-A blast...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 120,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Go away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 121,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,50)}Rap..."
 },
 {
  "i": 122,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You bastard..."
 },
 {
  "i": 123,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Deadly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 124,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Fire Bird Star!"
 },
 {
  "i": 125,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Damn!"
 },
 {
  "i": 126,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "This is so unfair!"
 },
 {
  "i": 127,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm unable to attack her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 128,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "But she can attack me back!"
 },
 {
  "i": 129,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What kind of matchup is this?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 130,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "M-Move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 131,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I can't see what's in front of me."
 },
 {
  "i": 132,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 133,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 134,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Ghost Rap..."
 },
 {
  "i": 135,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What's this...?"
 },
 {
  "i": 136,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's shameful..."
 },
 {
  "i": 137,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I thought that woman was weaker than me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 138,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Bear!"
 },
 {
  "i": 139,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Be careful,"
 },
 {
  "i": 140,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Kumashi's strength exceeds that of a common bear."
 },
 {
  "i": 141,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What's this...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 142,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "No one in the crew could stand up against that woman's ability...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 143,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "She was supposed to be someone only I could defeat...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 144,
  "style": "Flashbacks",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You can't..."
 },
 {
  "i": 145,
  "style": "Flashbacks",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You can't expect to beat her with your inferior abilities."
 },
 {
  "i": 146,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "This was supposed to be my chance... but look at me...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 147,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "No use..."
 },
 {
  "i": 148,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's no use!"
 },
 {
  "i": 149,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I have no chance to win!"
 },
 {
  "i": 150,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If I'm defeated here, she'll go capture Luffy and the others, then the crew will be finished..."
 },
 {
  "i": 151,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Saving them was a heavier burden than I thought...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 152,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Save me..."
 },
 {
  "i": 153,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Save me...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 154,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Sogeking!"
 },
 {
  "i": 155,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Please show me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 156,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What would you do?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 157,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}Oh, the wind carries my name"
 },
 {
  "i": 158,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}from Sniper Island far away."
 },
 {
  "i": 159,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}When I take aim, it is straight and true,"
 },
 {
  "i": 160,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}lu lu la la lu."
 },
 {
  "i": 161,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}Whether you're a man or a mouse:"
 },
 {
  "i": 162,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}Lock on!"
 },
 {
  "i": 163,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}I will put your heart in my sights,"
 },
 {
  "i": 164,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}Lock on!!"
 },
 {
  "i": 165,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\an8}The man who came from the Sniper Island..."
 },
 {
  "i": 166,
  "style": "Jungle P lyrics",
  "name": "Song",
  "text": "{\\fad(0,500}{\\an8}Lu lu lu lu lu la la!"
 },
 {
  "i": 167,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Kumashi!"
 },
 {
  "i": 168,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 169,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "You! How dare you hurt my Kumashi..!"
 },
 {
  "i": 170,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "What's with that stupid mask?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 171,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "There's nothing stupid about it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 172,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "Pleased to meet you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "My name is Sogeking!"
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Don't take me for a fool!"
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "You expect me to believe you're someone else?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "Time to run!"
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "And now you run?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "Calm down!"
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "Fight, Usopp-kun!"
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It's no use!"
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I can't win at all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "That's not true!"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "You're the only man who can do it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Do you even have a basis to support that?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "No."
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "So you don't!"
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Mini Hollow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "Just think for a second."
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sogeking",
  "text": "There's definitely something suspicious about that woman."
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That's for sure..."
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That woman became so confident all of a sudden."
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "At first she was afraid of me and ran away."
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If she was immune to my attacks, then she wouldn't need to run."
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "She could have flown or gone through walls."
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "But she was crying while running away instead."
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Rap!"
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Rap!"
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "The moment I lost track of that woman..."
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Something happened..."
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Back when I was dealing with the bear..."
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That's when I lost sight of her... for a moment."
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Well then, it's about time I take you to Moriah-sama."
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That's it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I've solved it...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Are there any suspicious places nearby...?"
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Like a secret room..."
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Your trick!"
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "What's that? Your last words?"
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Where are you aiming?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That's it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Hey, wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Deadly Atlas Meteor!"
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I've found it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That's your real body!"
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If you're capable of flying,"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "going through walls and people..."
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "changing from big to small as you please..."
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "that means your body is that of a ghost!"
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "But when I think of how you ran from me earlier..."
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Flashbacks",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Stay away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "At that time you were in your physical body!"
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "What do yo-"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Which means!"
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "The person before me..."
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Is merely a ghost you created while I took my eyes off you."
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You've kept your body concealed in there!"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You can't hide the truth anymore!"
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I thought you were just a negative idiot..."
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Did you draw courage from that stupid mask?"
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I'm surprised you could figure it out."
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "But you're only 90% right..."
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I'm not a ghost that can be controlled by my body..."
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I become separated from it through Astral Travel."
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "A hollow that can think and act for itself."
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I see!"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Then, without a body to return to,"
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I wonder what will happen to you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm sure you'd tell me not to attack it, right?"
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Bastard! Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Deadly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Great Explosion Star!"
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "That was close..."
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "You missed, though it was a dud."
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "One more shot!"
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Like I'd let you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Special Hollow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Is this a...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Mini Hollow..."
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Extra-large version of those things?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "This is bad!"
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Let go of me, bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Struggle for a while."
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I won't let you touch my real body."
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Wait a sec!"
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Those dumpling-sized ghosts already caused insane damage!"
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If this insanely huge thing explodes, my body'll be blown to pieces!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Struggle all you want, you can't touch it..."
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "It's a ghost."
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Let go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Let go of me, damn it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "It's a shame, Nega-nose."
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "When I snap my fingers, your body will be blown to pieces."
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Kamikaze Rap!"
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "It disappeared?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That was close."
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Your attack is now within this dial!"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "What do you-"
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I can't move!"
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "What is this?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "The Great Explosion Star I shot you with was a lie!"
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It wasn't a dud..."
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It was my Sticky Substance."
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "That way you wouldn't be able to move even if you returned to your real body."
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "What did you say?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Now I can take out both your body and hollow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Damn!"
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "So you're the rat who purified Commander Kumashi?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Just in time!"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Get him, Vice-commander Noble-hippo!"
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Impact!"
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Is this guy... truly that strong?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "It hurts!"
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm gonna lose my arm!"
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Noble-hippo!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Deadly..."
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Black Luster Star!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Cockroaches!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Also called Cockroach Star."
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Disgusting!"
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Someone get them off!"
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Help me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I can't get away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "It crawled inside my clothes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I hate cockroaches!"
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I'm scared, so scared!"
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Kumashi!"
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Don't get scared over simple cockroaches..."
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Your real nightmare is..."
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You underestimated me too much."
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "I'm a man best known in East Blue for my Super Strength!"
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "T-Ten ton...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "H-Hey, where did you get all that strength?"
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "S-Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "There's no way I'd survive that!"
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "That'd kill me, hey!"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Take the cockroaches away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Also take that hammer away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Take the cockroaches and the hammer away, please!"
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)\\pos(585,702)}Us"
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(1500,150)\\pos(621,702)}o"
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(50,150)\\pos(676,702)}pp..."
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "I won't lay a hand on your friends ever again!"
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Really! Really!"
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Please! Please! Usopp-sama!"
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Golden..."
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Pound!"
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "So, the Princess of a Haunted Mansion..."
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "can't help but faint over a balloon and some toy cockroaches."
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You were wrong..."
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If you thought you could beat me in a duel of negativity and lies!"
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Sweet dreams until daybreak!"
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Didn't that samurai just say something?"
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "In other words..."
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "what does this mean?"
 },
 {
  "i": 329,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "It means..."
 },
 {
  "i": 330,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "the match is over!"
 },
 {
  "i": 331,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
